{"tid":2130819,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭月娥禁止堂食有冇違反香港人權法案條例？","createTime":"2020-07-29T12:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:28.000Z","uid":34154,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81bc597a9c054f894fd6b6cc591957978eb8722a","tid":2130819,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"利申 唔係法律人士<br />\n香港有條法例叫做香港人權法案條例，第六條第一點話「自由被剝奪之人，應受合於人道及尊重其天賦人格尊嚴之處遇。」 英文係 All persons deprived of their liberty shall be treated with humanity and with respect for the inherent dignity of the human person.<br />\n<br />\n咁而家鄭月娥用防疫條例禁止堂食，即係以防疫為由剝削咗香港人喺餐廳堂食嘅自由，但係就搞到好多人要好冇尊嚴咁隨地甚至喺廁所食飯<br />\n咁係咪即係違反咗香港人權法案條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥講到連黨安法都唔會侵犯到香港人嘅人權同自由<br />\n咁點解防疫就可以剝削尊嚴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇法律巴絲可以解答吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係違反咗香港人權法案條例，係咪可以司法覆核？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨安法就話夾硬改基本法寫到不受司法覆核，但係防疫條例應該冇咁寫啦掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99de0064ac2e33f20d3a5b47fe732ac659a91729","tid":2130819,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc997efa7f27c2c829876a15443a5f7af0d03ce1","tid":2130819,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f010bdaad4518bd6686743dc0f23829615825a","tid":2130819,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"國安法行先"},{"pid":"f9a637ea0d28d68c159717b1a64ee718c0d33f54","tid":2130819,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"冇  <br />\n因為林鄭月娥無禁公務員食堂<br />\n只係&quot;少數人&quot;無得堂食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d989972f50601e9727df347c7145d75def4630","tid":2130819,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9a637ea0d28d68c159717b1a64ee718c0d33f54","tid":2130819,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"冇  <br />\n因為林鄭月娥無禁公務員食堂<br />\n只係&quot;少數人&quot;無得堂食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}